# Lyndon words.

# Next Lyndon word by Duval's algorithm.
Next ← (
  ˜↙/⊂⊸˜↯              # Repeat len times, cut to length.
  ⊙⊸⊣                  # Get last of alphabet for comparisons.
  ⊙◌⍢(↘¯1|⨬(0|=⊣)>1⊸⧻) # While len>1 and last = alph last, truncate.
  ⊂⊙(⊡+1⊸˜⨂⊢)⊃↘↙¯1     # Replace final char with successor.
)
Step ← ◡(°□⋅⋅⊣)⊃(⋅⊙∘|˜⊂□Next)
Prep ← ⊃(⋅↙₁|⊙∘|{⋅↙₁})
# All Lyndon words up to given length. (len; alphabet) -> {words}
Lyndon ← ◌◌◌⍢(Step|¬≍⊓(↙¯1|°□⊣)⋅⋅⊙∘)Prep
Lyndon 5 "01"
